Rollout context: user had already seeded demo accounts + curriculum but login still failed because `/api/auth/login`/`/api/auth/session` were hitting the proxy and being redirected back to `/auth/login`, preventing the handlers from running.

User preferences: none explicit aside from adherence to existing conductor/TDD guidance implied by instructions (used plan updates, tests before code changes).

