Outcome: success

Key steps:
- Confirmed README documents seeding `npx convex run seed:seedDemoAccounts` + `npx convex run seed:seedPublishedCurriculum`; `convex/seed.ts` exports seed helpers and alias `seedUnit1Lesson1` for the published curriculum (refs in README + seed file).[/home/daniel-bo/Desktop/bus-math-v2/README.md#L78][convex/seed.ts#L350-364]
