+# Implementation Plan
+
+## Phase 1: Launch Contract Guards
+
+- [ ] Task: Add regression tests for launch-critical auth and local runtime behavior
+  - [ ] Extend proxy coverage so unauthenticated login and session bootstrap APIs must remain public
+  - [ ] Extend Convex admin-auth coverage so local development accepts both project-local and home-directory Convex state
+  - [ ] Extend dev-stack coverage so the pinned Convex CLI and parent-process startup contract are enforced
+- [ ] Task: Add guard coverage for launch documentation and deployment expectations
+  - [ ] Add source-level tests that fail if the active Cloudflare launch checklist or runtime docs lose required secret, seeding, or verification guidance
+  - [ ] Mark the new track active in Conductor and capture implementation status
+
+## Phase 2: Runtime and Documentation Hardening
+
+- [ ] Task: Harden auth bootstrap and local Convex runtime wiring
+  - [ ] Keep the public proxy allowlist aligned with login/session bootstrap requirements
+  - [ ] Align server-side Convex admin auth and local development docs with the supported `convex dev --local` workflow
+- [ ] Task: Publish the active Cloudflare launch checklist
+  - [ ] Add a launch checklist document under the active `conductor/` surface
+  - [ ] Link README and architecture/runtime docs to the checklist and operational expectations
+
+## Phase 3: Verification and Finalization
+
+- [ ] Task: Synchronize Conductor memory for the launch-hardening outcome
+  - [ ] Update `conductor/tech-debt.md` and `conductor/lessons-learned.md` with any remaining near-term implications
+  - [ ] Update track metadata/status markers as execution progresses
+- [ ] Task: Run required verification and finalize the track
+  - [ ] Run `npm run lint`
+  - [ ] Run `npm test`
+  - [ ] Run `npm run build`
